high_descs: Walk towards the opposite end of the kitchen and then turn right to find a fork on the counter.
Pick up the fork from the counter.
Turn left to face the pan on the counter.
Open the cabinet below the pan and place the fork in the cup in the cabinet.
Take out the cup from the cabinet.
Turn left and walk a few steps and then turn right to face the sink.
Place the cup in the sink in between the pot and another cup.
anns.task_desc: Put the dirty fork in a cup to place it in the sink.

high_descs: Walk to the fridge in front of you
Grab the fork next to the fridge
Open the cabinet below you
Place the fork in the cup
Grab the cup from the shelf
Walk to the sink to your left
Place the cup inside of the sink
anns.task_desc: Place the fork and cup in the sink

high_descs: go over to the kitchen counter left of the fridge

pick up that same cup with the fork in it
